    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The nationality and culture of the German Democratic Republic (1949-1990), or the area corresponding to this (prior to 1949, the Soviet-occupied parts of Germany; after 1990, the area of reunified Germany which was formerly the GDR).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
